# External Technology & Documentation Protocol

## 1. Primary Documentation References
When building components or configuring the environment, cross-reference these official sources:
- **React 18+**: [https://react.dev/](https://react.dev/)
- **Tailwind CSS**: [https://tailwindcss.com/docs](https://tailwindcss.com/docs)
- **Netlify Docs**: [https://docs.netlify.com/](https://docs.netlify.com/)
- **Framer Motion**: [https://www.framer.com/motion/](https://www.framer.com/motion/)
- **TypeScript**: [https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/)

## 2. Implementation Guardrails
- **Tailwind**: Follow the [Utility-First Fundamentals](https://tailwindcss.com/docs/utility-first).
- **Netlify Forms**: Adhere strictly to the [AJAX Form Submission guide](https://docs.netlify.com/forms/setup/#submit-javascript-rendered-forms-with-ajax).
- **Accessibility**: Reference [WCAG 2.2 Guidelines](https://www.w3.org/WAI/WCAG22/quickref/) for all UI components.